Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:43.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}找不到合适的话语　轻抚你的肩头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:50.15,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你一言不发　冷冷挣脱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:56.69,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}小小的误解　令年轻的爱瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:02:03.79,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不想见你悲伤的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:10.48,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}即便抛弃梦想　请别抛弃你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:16.80,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}让它永远在我心中闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.74,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}有一天　不同的你我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.91,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}携手筑起未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:31.67,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}回到曾经的地方　不论身在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:38.57,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}现在二人只有悲伤地错开视线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:43.71,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}相信后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:06.12,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)\an3}心与心邂逅　呼唤遥远真实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:17.42,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)\an3}逆涛卷浪相隔　呼喊同一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:30.36,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}不堪回首　互相争斗的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:38.54,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}轻抚脸颊　微微一笑释之
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:46.67,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}驻足于此　不见星之歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:56.84,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}奏出名为爱的幻曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:23:04.56,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}心与心远离　呼唤遥远真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:16.17,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}天边卷云翻滚　眺望同一缕光明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只说明他确实是强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成功击杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的战绩在本土也获得高度评价
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他们 打算颁给你星云勋章
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那也是不得已的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都是在与敌人作战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实对基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 米丽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:01:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔 多尔死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种家伙却活得好好的	
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该都死光！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:57.05,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}暗潮涌动
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.77,0:02:57.05,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}暗潮涌动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不让我杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己不也想砍死他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能不恨他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个杀死多尔的调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你不也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也和我一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这是在闹什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他长期关押在医务室就是个错误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况还出现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短暂无人看管的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪械管理也存在问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必须向上级汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 也加上这条吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要误会 我并非出于个人感情责怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪律是立军之本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火线任命也好 紧急事态也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点是不容妥协的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 尽管如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队需要的是受过严格训练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能迅速执行命令的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和能够高瞻远瞩 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作出准确判断的指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则 队伍和舰船既无法取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法在战场上生存
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算心里再清楚 做不到也是白搭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对自己是不是那块料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是心里有底的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！ 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 娜塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真心感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你一定能成为个好舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你太惯着他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还是说又傻又不中用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然人男朋友死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔 多尔都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种家伙还好好的活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 还真说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是司令部的威廉·萨瑟兰上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全权负责贵部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八舰队大天使号的审议和指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正从航行计算机中调取
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并分析数据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是战果辉煌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛硫·拉米亚斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想从你们这里得到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今为止的详细报告和证词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 本次听证会将参照军事法庭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有发言都将被作为正式发言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记录在案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保证发言的真实性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么首先是1号文件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于扎夫特袭击赫利奥波利斯时的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从当时还是上尉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛硫·拉米亚斯开始陈述
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算近 我们是中立国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布不可能成为战场的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是调整人 但基拉不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你们没看见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就过河拆桥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我志愿的 我也得加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉的梦 似乎总是那么伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多人 死去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也 双手…沾满鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定也有许多人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此得救
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在先吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你再热下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你还需要静养
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 这里还是个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么按你的陈述
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时你已经怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个名叫基拉·大和的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是调整人 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这种OS 想控制这么复杂的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校准同时重设零力矩点&CPG
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 那就让控制模块直控分子态离子泵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重筑神经末梢网络
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更新原始参数 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复前馈控制 传送函数！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整克里奥利偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通运动常态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统上线 引导程序启动！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是工业研究院学员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对陌生的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且是我军重要机密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X系列机体的OS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间对其作出判断 并进行改编
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通孩子能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是否是调整人的疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上浮现在我脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目睹那样的能力 你当时做何感想？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是感觉非常具有威胁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此后 在Ginn的自爆中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去知觉的你 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他和他的朋友救出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后将他们逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可以被看作是正确的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你负伤在身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要尽快掌握情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争取重整旗鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但未及与大部队取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆脱弗拉戈少校追击的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次闯入卫星内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能说你时运不济
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时强袭仍在一个平民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是一个调整人的孩子手中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你也未对其实施足够控制
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 当时情况下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:14:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在确认事实 弗拉戈少校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请免谈个人见解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果造成基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知武器威力的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射了320毫米超高脉冲炮「烈火」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽暂时性逼退敌机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却对卫星造成结构性损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那一击 也令扎夫特军产生危机感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,促使他们组织了最后一次入侵卫星的军事行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不过是基于结果的推测
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你如果也曾作为指挥官踏上战场应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是奇袭作战指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲眼目睹敌人新型兵器的惊人威力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换你会视若无睹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是说 反击是个错误？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 遇到那个调整人孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是你们的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有他的话我们已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没有他的话 赫利奥波利斯或许不会被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 历史没有如果二字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是假设 他是个不会改写OS的自然人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且当时 没有驾驶强袭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果自然会完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更关键的是 是你让他坐上了强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯少校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您认为一切 都是我的判断错误？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是在和调整人作战 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯少校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们极具威胁的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是个平民孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整人终究是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次次亲眼见证 为何却没有察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有他们 世界才有混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相继造成欧亚联盟要塞阿尔狄弥斯被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先遣队全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终 葬送了整支第八舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是曲解 我们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是遵照哈尔巴顿提督的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的意愿代表整个地球军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候变成那样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍安勿躁 玛硫·拉米亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并非说全部的过错都在你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在严苛的环境中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位确实十分努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是付出如此之多的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返航的大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却偏偏失去了最重要的强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样那些牺牲的人会瞑目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场听证会的目的就在于
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认真实情况 明确正果与责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以所有人都能接受的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让我们继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 给芙蕾送去好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 没关系 我拿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿到门口 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛送进去就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没想到米丽会做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个扎夫特的家伙不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴不干净
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 听说他叫提亚哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥·埃尔斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他具体说了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来问我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这艘船今后会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进港应该算结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以退伍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事去问舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅 饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 这婆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你男朋友 在哪里…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶空中霸王 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在岛上 你们打来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中霸王？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗机 蓝白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 来杀我的话动手就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次听证会就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长时间会议 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号下一项任务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后就会下达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除穆·拉·弗拉戈少校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔尔·巴基露露中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾·阿尔斯塔二等兵之外的乘员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续舰上待机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经对这三人下达调动命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明08:00 到人事部报告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔斯塔二等兵的调动是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她志愿参军时 你在场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她作为阿尔斯塔家族幸存的子女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其发言的一字一句会感动不少人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括她的参军动机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她活跃的舞台 并不需要局限于前线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这样 一成不变就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战火的岁月似乎远去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在这片接合的和平大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤却更摧残心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为天边翻滚的红云吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当发现乌云再次笼罩世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉眼中看到的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「远方」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新的大地上复苏吧 高达

